IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. CUSTORDBM.
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
       FILE-CONTROL.
           SELECT SYSIN ASSIGN TO SYSIN.
       DATA DIVISION.
       FILE SECTION.
       FD  SYSIN RECORD CONTAINS 80 CHARACTERS.
       01  SYSIN-REC PIC X(80).
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  WS-CMD    PIC X(20) VALUE SPACES.
       01  CUSTOMER-SEG.
           05 CUSTID     PIC X(10).
           05 CUSTNAME   PIC X(40).
           05 ADDRESS    PIC X(50).
       01  ORDER-SEG.
           05 ORDID      PIC X(10).
           05 ORDDATE    PIC X(8).
           05 AMOUNT     PIC S9(7)V99 COMP-3.
           05 STATUS     PIC X(10).
       LINKAGE SECTION.
       01  IO-PCB  PIC X(24).
       01  DB-PCB.
           05 FILLER PIC X(8).
           05 DB-STATUS PIC X(2).
           05 FILLER PIC X(8).
           05 SEG-LEVEL PIC S9(4) COMP.
           05 KEY-LEN   PIC S9(4) COMP.
           05 SEG-NAME  PIC X(8).
           05 KEY-FB    PIC X(200).
       PROCEDURE DIVISION USING IO-PCB DB-PCB.
       MAIN.
           DISPLAY 'CUSTORDBM STARTED'.
           READ SYSIN AT END MOVE 'RUNALL' TO WS-CMD END-READ.
           DISPLAY 'COMMAND=' WS-CMD.
           GOBACK.
